\v 7 Então, <a name="01700500700004" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">respondeu</a> <a name="01700500700006" ll="SDBH:אֶסְתֵּר:000000">Ester</a> e <a name="01700500700010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: <a name="01700500700012" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֵלָה:000000">Minha</a> <a name="01700500700012" ll="SDBH:שְׁאֵלָה:000000">petição</a> e <a name="01700500700016" ll="SDBH:בַּקָּשָׁה:000000">desejo</a> são o seguinte: 
